# Sketching ruins in the dark. #

51:32.720 --> 51:34.040
HE PANTS

51:38.520 --> 51:40.000
Nice dog.

51:44.640 --> 51:49.919
In 1588, a ship from the
Spanish Armada was wrecked on Skye,

51:49.920 --> 51:53.000
and the only survivors
were three white dogs.

51:54.760 --> 51:57.519
Clan Donald took them, fed them,

51:57.520 --> 51:59.799
kept them away from
the local mongrels

51:59.800 --> 52:01.920
and bred them for centuries.

52:03.880 --> 52:06.519
They called them
West Highland Terriers,

52:06.520 --> 52:09.560
and they kept them
a secret for 200 years.

52:11.440 --> 52:14.760
You can keep anything secret
if you work hard enough.

52:21.760 --> 52:24.840
Someone told me yesterday
I wasn't capable of guilt.

52:26.680 --> 52:28.359
And he was right.

52:28.360 --> 52:30.799
Feelings like that -

52:30.800 --> 52:34.519
guilt, love, happiness -

52:34.520 --> 52:36.360
they don't touch the sides.

52:38.280 --> 52:41.159
I've always needed something...

52:41.160 --> 52:43.040
..more, something deeper.

52:45.080 --> 52:47.399
When I was young, it was fear.

52:47.400 --> 52:49.999
Fear of being found out,

52:50.000 --> 52:52.999
being discovered in worlds
I didn't belong in,

52:53.000 --> 52:55.320
I didn't have the breeding for.

53:01.800 --> 53:04.200
Then fear turned to greed.

53:08.080 --> 53:10.520
And that did a decent
job for me, too.

53:13.080 --> 53:15.519
In prison,

53:15.520 --> 53:17.720
