53:20.960 --> 53:22.480
..I was lost.

53:27.600 --> 53:29.480
I was twisting in the wind.

53:32.360 --> 53:34.640
I tried guilt, don't get me wrong.

53:37.840 --> 53:39.360
How could I not?

53:42.720 --> 53:45.919
Late at night,
lying in a cell in the dark,

53:45.920 --> 53:47.400
you'll try anything.

53:52.520 --> 53:55.599
But it didn't work,

53:55.600 --> 53:58.799
because guilt's about looking back

53:58.800 --> 54:01.199
and what I needed,
what I've always needed

54:01.200 --> 54:03.840
is something that can help me now.

54:05.280 --> 54:07.240
Something to drive me.

54:13.840 --> 54:16.080
Something to grant me purpose.

54:17.560 --> 54:19.400
Because a man like me...

54:20.840 --> 54:22.920
..he needs something to draw on.

54:24.840 --> 54:27.320
A man like me, he needs some...

54:29.000 --> 54:30.720
..heavy fuel.

54:32.680 --> 54:34.600
And then you came to see me.

54:36.720 --> 54:38.160
And I found it.

54:39.800 --> 54:41.879
What I needed.

54:41.880 --> 54:44.039
Thank God.

54:44.040 --> 54:45.840
I found it.

54:55.720 --> 54:57.320
Revenge.

55:06.760 --> 55:08.520
It's revenge.

